      "amount": "a few sprigs (optional)"
    },
    {
      "name": "sugar or fish sauce (optional)",
      "amount": "1/4 to 1/2 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Bring the vegetable broth and water or stock to a boil.",
    "Add blanched garlic cloves, salt, pepper, sugar or fish sauce, and sesame oil to taste. Stir well.",
    "Reduce heat to low and let simmer for about 10 minutes.",
    "Add chopped spinach leaves and continue to cook until the spinach is wilted.",
    "Stir in fresh cilantro if desired.",
    "Serve hot."
